dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:200,000 scale maps of Central Primorskiĭ kraĭ (Russia), titled 'Primorskiĭ kraĭ -- 沿海州中部/Primorskiĭ kraĭ.’To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
